# tanliumei.github.io 谭镠美博客 # First [参考网站](http://blog.csdn.net/renfufei/article/details/37725057/) `
import vte; import gtk v = vte.Terminal () v.connect ("child-exited", lambda term: gtk.main_quit()) v.fork_command() window = gtk.Window() window.add(v) window.connect('delete-event', lambda window, event: gtk.main_quit()) window.show_all()
